title: Stevie J Interview
itunes:title: Stevie J Interview
description:
One half of Sleazo and Zino from Love and Hip Hop Atlanta, Stevie J. stopped by the Breakfast Club to talk about his new reality show, his drama with Joseline Hernandez and finding out if he's the baby's daddy. He's working on a new album with Faith Evans...but are they making more than music? Plus he addresses statements made by Young Dro when he came to the Breakfast Club. Charlamagne gives the Donkey to a Trump, but its not the President Elect!
